  <entry>
    <title>c++学习笔记</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2020/10/10/C++%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2020/10/10/C++%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E7%AC%94%E8%AE%B0/</id>
    <published>2020-10-10T01:41:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-10-18T15:03:46.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="关于判断输入是否正确并提示用户重新输入直至正确的方法"><a href="#关于判断输入是否正确并提示用户重新输入直至正确的方法" class="headerlink" title="关于判断输入是否正确并提示用户重新输入直至正确的方法"></a>关于判断输入是否正确并提示用户重新输入直至正确的方法</h3><p>题目：用户输入年龄判断输入是否合法直至输入成功</p><p><strong>方法一：使用goto语句(不推荐)</strong></p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Again: <span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;Enter your age: &quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">cin</span> &gt;&gt; age;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(age &lt; <span class="number">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;Error, exprct input an integer(&gt;0)&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="built_in">endl</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">goto</span> Again;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>方法二：使用while循环控制</strong></p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">bool</span> isWrong = <span class="literal">true</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(isWrong)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;Enter your age: &quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">cin</span> &gt;&gt; age;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> (age &gt; <span class="number">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">            isWrong = <span class="literal">false</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;<span class="keyword">else</span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;Error, exprct input an integer(&gt;0)&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="built_in">endl</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="书写浮点数"><a href="#书写浮点数" class="headerlink" title="书写浮点数"></a>书写浮点数</h3><p>除了使用小数点书写小数，还可以通过科学技术法书写，这对于使用极小浮点数有好处。</p><p>例如当我需要声明一个小数值为0.00000000000000000911，我可以直接声明</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">double</span> b = <span class="number">0.00000000000000000911</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>更简单的表达方法是</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">double</span> a = <span class="number">9.11e-18</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="结构数组"><a href="#结构数组" class="headerlink" title="结构数组"></a>结构数组</h3><p>c++支持对结构对象创建数组，其方法与创建普通数组类似</p><p>例如现在我拥有一个名为person的结构体</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">person</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">char</span> name[<span class="number">20</span>];</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> age;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>我可以通过类似声明数组的方式一次性初始化多个person类型的元素</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">person stdent[<span class="number">2</span>] = &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;<span class="string">&quot;Alice&quot;</span>, <span class="number">20</span>&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">        &#123;<span class="string">&quot;Rylaris&quot;</span>, <span class="number">13</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;h3 id=&quot;关于判断输入是否正确并提示用户重新输入直至正确的方法&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#关于判断输入是否正确并提示用户重新输入直至正确的方法&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;关于判断输入是否正确并提示用户重新输入直至正确的方法&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;关于判断输入是否</summary>
      
    
    
    
